{"tid":2249113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度手足！  暗諷係支那抄襲大國","createTime":"2020-10-19T06:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T06:19:28.000Z","uid":374134,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab464a03408c90f118ee83d6096a078c8bab3250","tid":2249113,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsNFdCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsNFdCy.jpg&h=7e65d80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度一名男子日前在推特上分享一張照片，為一位學生的英文作業，其中題目要求寫出「Original（原創；原始的）」的反義詞，沒想到學生卻在空格填入「China（中國）」，似乎有在暗諷中國是抄襲大國的意味，不過這個答案隨之被糾正，而此圖一出也馬上引發熱議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/susantananda3/status/1317337059112091655?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsusantananda3%2Fstatus%2F1317337059112091655%3Fs%3D21&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=a8abfa40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsusantananda3%2Fstatus%2F1317337059112091655%3Fs%3D21&h=ad50938b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/susantananda3/status/1317337059112091655?s=21</a><br />\n該答案隨之被老師打上一個大叉，並改正為「Artificial（人造的）」，南達於是好奇向廣大鄉民發問，「這個是誰對？老師還是學生？<br />\n貼文一出隨即掀起熱議，不少網友認為，「學生是對的，Artificial是舊的反義詞，China才是新的」、「好聰明，我完全沒想過會有這個答案」、「老師是依照單字去糾正，而學生的答案則是依照他的心去寫的」、「2013年就有這樣的認知，這學生肯定是人才」、「在武漢肺炎後學生肯定是錯的，因為中國是原創的」；另外也有人指出，「老師是錯的，Original的反義詞應該是Fake（假的；偽造的）」。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=832860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D832860&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=39679ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D832860&h=5aee5d86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=832860</a>"},{"pid":"80636d58635e2abc82cf4d43d4c2b2d1dd4da4e7","tid":2249113,"uid":153144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150ab067648ff517da0f68d19b55ae3bcb881472","tid":2249113,"uid":153144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341d1c8334cfb13d97ae0e0fed723272df36ccca","tid":2249113,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f31f73c5ba6e15e66e38daa752ba369d0d1978","tid":2249113,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"2013"},{"pid":"0eeb699426c233d752f254c888bf676fad9e346d","tid":2249113,"uid":165079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:17:17.000Z","msg":"Artificial 反義詞係 natural<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c4180c1b0da893079f247a5b6a587b3973232","tid":2249113,"uid":153035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"其實錯在詞性，填Chinese就啱"}],"pinned":{"pid":"738c4180c1b0da893079f247a5b6a587b3973232","tid":2249113,"uid":153035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"其實錯在詞性，填Chinese就啱"}}